data.title: Tanya Andrews Obituary 2016

data.text:
Tanya Lee Andrews, 53, of Davenport, died Saturday, January 2, 2016 at Select Specialty Hospital in Davenport.

A memorial service celebrating her life will be held at 11:00 a.m. on Thursday, January 7, 2016 at Church of the Cross United Methodist Church in Port Byron, Illinois. Memorials may be made to the family.

Born on July 26, 1962 in Davenport, Tanya was the daughter of Joseph Andrews, Jr. and Sandra Johnson Charlan.

Tanya enjoyed playing BINGO and spending time with her family.

Those left to honor her memory include her sons, Joshua (Andrea) Andrews of Bettendorf, Jeff (Alli) Andrews of Clarksville, Tennessee, and Kai, Kel and D.J. Andrews of Davenport; grandchildren, Ricky, Athena, Kailah and Laila; sister, Becky Andrews of Lost Nation; brother, Joseph Andrews III of Davenport; and a special nephew, Jay.

She was received in heaven by her father, Joseph.
